data.description: Enjoy Country Club Living in this charming condo with wrap around deck overlooking a gorgeous lake  ***   The Villages Golf & Country Club, a gated ,senior community located in the Evergreen Hills of Silicon Valley, next to Silver Creek Country Club *** NOTE: One resident must be 55+ ***  This spacious 1571sf condo has 2 large bedrooms plus a den (for those who work from home) 2 full bathrooms, inside laundry room, bright kitchen with nook ***  spacious living room and dining room with lovely chandelier ***  Imagine sitting on your porch overlooking the pristine lake with beautiful sunsets or at night viewing the moon and stars *** Soooo relaxing and peaceful *** Some of the amenities living within The Villages include: 2 Golf Courses, Tennis, Pickleball, Bocce, Ping-Pong, Billiards, Hiking trails and modern Fitness Center *** Dine in our formal dining room overlooking the golf course or The Bistro with patio service ***  THIS WONDERFUL, ACTIVE, ADULT COMMUNITY IS WAITING JUST FOR YOU.
